                      and
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                Check the new rules for your type of goods 
              </span>
</h3>          </div>

          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-check-the-new-rules-for-your-type-of-goods-3">
              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">From 1 January 2021, the rules for importing some types of goods will change. </p>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="3">
<li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.1" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/import-licences-and-certificates-from-1-january-2021?step-by-step-nav=1ddb4c89-1fe9-4ad0-b561-c1b0158e6bc5">Check what import licences or certificates you need </a></li>
<li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.2" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/labelling-and-marketing-standards-from-1-january-2021?step-by-step-nav=1ddb4c89-1fe9-4ad0-b561-c1b0158e6bc5">Check the labelling and marketing standards for food, plant seeds and manufactured goods </a></li>
<li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.3" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/importing-excise-goods-from-the-eu-in-a-no-deal-brexit?step-by-step-nav=1ddb4c89-1fe9-4ad0-b561-c1b0158e6bc5">Check the rules for importing alcohol, tobacco and certain oils </a></li>
</ol>

          </div>

        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-step-nav__step js-step
