                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                Make sure you have an EORI number starting with GB
              </span>
</h3>          </div>

          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-make-sure-you-have-an-eori-number-starting-with-gb-4">
              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">You need an EORI number that starts with GB to import goods from 1 January 2021.</p>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="1"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="4.1" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/eori?step-by-step-nav=1ddb4c89-1fe9-4ad0-b561-c1b0158e6bc5">Get an EORI number </a></li></ol>

