                Check if you can make the importing process quicker
              </span>
</h3>          </div>

          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-check-if-you-can-make-the-importing-process-quicker-6">
              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">From 1 January 2021, you'll need to make customs declarations when you import goods from the EU, Switzerland, Norway, Iceland and Liechtenstein. </p>

              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">In some situations, you can delay making a declaration for up to 6 months after you imported the goods. </p>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="1"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item gem-c-step-nav__list-item--active"><a data-position="6.1" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="#content"><span class="gem-c-step-nav__link-active-context visuallyhidden">You are currently viewing: </span>Check if you can declare your goods later to make the importing process quicker </a></li></ol>

